{"tid":1141352,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[小島秀夫點讚] 動作遊戲新作《UNDEFEATED》即將在Steam平台免費推出","createTime":"2019-05-06T12:12:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T23:08:02.000Z","uid":75050,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"22ae91feef0b03da7aa401188defeec84b241d96","tid":1141352,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"【不用擔心，因為，我！來了！】<br />\n曾獲小島秀夫點讚轉發的動作遊戲新作《UNDEFEATED》即將在Steam平台免費推出。<br />\n<br />\n據制作者ユーマ的介紹，《UNDEFEATED》是由他和其他同學在學生時代制作的作品，如今包括他在內的幾人均已在春季畢業，進入了不同的遊戲公司工作。<br />\n<br />\nユーマ表示本作是他出於自身興趣制作的作品，完全沒有想要從中賺錢的念頭，因此這款作品將會在未來免費推出。<br />\n<br />\nTwitter：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/UMA_Hero_16/status/1123188731597352960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUMA_Hero_16%2Fstatus%2F1123188731597352960&d=9OMcXw0STyGFZrzowU4xHoGitI067obQ02bu1xQE4oc%3D&h=016330db\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FUMA_Hero_16%2Fstatus%2F1123188731597352960&h=8c97e1ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/UMA_Hero_16/status/1123188731597352960</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1RAbx0k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1RAbx0k.jpg&h=efe1fe15&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a8aaa30eab42d1865954df8e52c8e158b7e94d62","tid":1141352,"uid":37573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T12:20:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19734550ca177951b8c02c2b45eb360762c8c44c","tid":1141352,"uid":75050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T14:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"975feaebe3c6f2137770e298fa942fe019c6a73b","tid":1141352,"uid":34395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"咁似saint row<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e66ea1f7affc0266876